{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c94d6a6958","title":"毛泽东对邓小平在七届六中全会上的发言稿的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"51a84e528f","index":0,"year":1955,"month":10,"day":7,"articleId":"c94d6a6958"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3c4fdd599e","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对邓小平在七届六中全会上的发言稿的批语和修改","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"5453d60582","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"3136dbee84","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"329db45c4b","type":"paragraph","text":"退邓小平同志。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"69385c3c04","type":"paragraph","text":"此件很好。作了一点修改，请你斟酌。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"bc97c64614","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十月七日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"8ca0444d03","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"e38be55aad","type":"paragraph","text":"[在对于农业社会主义改造抱着右倾观点的共产党员中，确有]一些[同资产阶级共呼吸的人]，他们是对资产阶级思想的投降主义者[。他们中的多数]则是反映[富裕中农的]思想。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"46d939aa00","type":"paragraph","text":"注：[ ]外为毛泽东加写或改写的文字。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"00aed47733","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"},{"id":"cbd8cf05f7","type":"paragraph","text":"一切在这个问题上犯右倾错误的同志，因为他们同党外的资产阶级思想有某些共同点，他们在资产阶级分子向党进攻的时候，就会丧失警觉，解除武装，不能理直气壮地驳斥资产阶级分子的谬论。例如在一九五三年，党内党外都有人叫喊所谓“农民苦”，而在一九五五年，党内党外又都有人叫喊所谓“农民生产情绪低落”，我们怎样能够希望这样的同志去理直气壮地驳斥党外的那些谬论呢?","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958"}],"page":{"id":"81f956a2b6","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c94d6a6958","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}